description:
Celena Cross is young, incredibly sexy, and has the tightest, hottest, most nubile body around. She comes to Hogtied for her first bondage experience and unfortunately discovers this type of thing is not for her. Hogtied is a lot of things and one of those things is honesty, so while Celena managed to struggle though her first three scenes we decided to call the shoot. She gave it her best and suffered a lot for someone at her level, but this kind of thing was just not for her.

Incidentally, we were shooting a BEHIND KINK story that followed her the entire day because we wanted to capture the real story of an inexperienced girl doing hogtied. I have included that episode of BEHIND KINK as an addition bonus so you can see what went on behind the camera. Think of it as our little Christmas gift to you.
title: Celena Cross
